  "description": "Low density — 0.18 — with large grains 0.8 and near-zero posScatter 0.05. The effect is sparse, meditational: one grain arrives, plays, completes, then silence before the next. pitchScatter 0, filter closed low. This is granular synthesis at its most honest — just a thing that pulses at the bottom, slowly, making no argument for its own existence.",
